WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.480 --> 00:00:06.234
We've set up a simple way for you to give to our&nbsp;church online.

00:00:06.234 --> 00:00:09.534
If you want to give a quick gift enter an amount, 

00:00:09.534 --> 00:00:15.667
select a fund, then enter your&nbsp;email address
 and your first and last name.

00:00:16.640 --> 00:00:21.400
Then, enter your payment details and&nbsp;
click give. And that's it! 

00:00:22.034 --> 00:00:28.160
We'll send a receipt to your email address. To use a saved&nbsp;
payment method or manage a recurring donation&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:28.160 --> 00:00:33.120
you'll want to log in. Click the login button and&nbsp;
we'll send a code to your phone or email account.

00:00:34.240 --> 00:00:39.040
Verify the code and you're in! 
Now&nbsp;your payment info is ready to go&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:39.040 --> 00:00:41.034
when you want to make a donation.

00:00:41.034 --> 00:00:44.867
To manage your giving details 
switch over to the my giving page. 

00:00:45.034 --> 00:00:49.680
Here you'll see more ways you&nbsp;can give. 
You can also add a payment method,&nbsp;

00:00:49.680 --> 00:00:55.534
a bank account or a debit card, set up a recurring&nbsp;
donation and view your giving history.

00:00:55.867 --> 00:01:01.600
To get started visit our website or download the church&nbsp;
center app in your android or apple app store.

